title: Dark Bunny
description: In the rain-drenched streets of Dark City, where the sun never rises, only one person stands between crime and humanity.
alt1: Dark Bunny faces off against Bananomanoman, an anthropomorphized banana
alt2: a rat Joker and a Catwoman lookalike
alt3: Dark Bunny fights against three of Clown Face's henchmen
alt4: Dark Bunny shakes hands with the commissioner
